name: Annie Lederman
bio: Annie can most recently been seen as a cast member on MTV's GIRL CODE and as the voice of Cheryl on GRAND THEFT AUTO 5. Annie Lederman also starred in WE HAVE ISSUES, a pop-culture talk show on E! with co-host Julian McCullough. She has also recently appeared on THIS IS NOT HAPPENING on Comedy Central, CHELSEA LATELY, @MIDNIGHT on Comedy Central, THE SOUP INVESTIGATES and ADAM DEVINE'S HOUSE PARTY.Â  In addition, Annie starred and wrote, STAND UPS, a scripted Comedy Central pilot, produced by Dan Powell (co-creator of INSIDE AMY SCHUMER), with comedians Kurt Metzger & Monroe Martin. She tours regularly worldwide as a stand-up comedian.
